'''Hilton Kelley''' is a former American actor and environmentalist from [[Port Arthur, Texas|Port Arthur]], Texas.<ref>{{cite web |first=Vicky |last=Wolf |url=http://www.cleanhouston.org/heros/kelley.htm | title=Hilton Kelley: Standing up for the West Side  |year=2006 | publisher=cleanhouston.org | accessdate=31 May 2012}}</ref> He was awarded the [[Goldman Environmental Prize]] in 2011, for his fight against pollution of the  [[Port Arthur, Texas|Port Arthur]] district from petrochemical industry and waste facilities.<ref>{{cite news |first=Carmen K. |last=Sisson  |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Making-a-difference/2011/0418/Hilton-Kelley-helps-clean-up-Texas-Gulf-Coast-town | title=Hilton Kelley helps clean up Texas Gulf Coast town  |date=18 April 2011 | journal=The Christian Science Monitor | accessdate=31 May 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Victoria |last=Gill |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/earth/hi/earth_news/newsid_9451000/9451460.stm | title=Goldman Prize: Zimbabwe's rhino rescuer honoured |date=11 April 2011 | newspaper=BBC News | accessdate=31 May 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldmanprize.org/pressroom/2011_print/pressreleases |title=2011 Goldman Environmental Prize Recipients |publisher=[[Goldman Environmental Prize]] |accessdate=30 May 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604225246/http://www.goldmanprize.org/pressroom/2011_print/pressreleases |archivedate=4 June 2012 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldmanprize.org/pressroom/2011_print/bios/northamerica |title=2011 Recipient for North America: Hilton Kelley |publisher=[[Goldman Environmental Prize]]|accessdate=30 May 2012}}</ref>

