{{clear}} ==CEO== The Luxgen 7 CEO is an executive limousine built on the MPV platform. Most parts of the vehicle body remains the same while on the exterior, the CEO receives a different grille design. It has two "first-class" rear seats with massage, recline and leg rest. A divider with motorized panels separates the passenger and driver compartments. The glass window can be [[frosted glass|frosted]] with the flick of a switch, along with an opaque panel that enhances privacy.
